There is so much talent on that team and Kaepernick has thrown 10 touchdowns to six different receivers. You can't predict where he is going to throw the ball because stats show he is capable of throwing to anyone. They have also got Frank Gore at running back, who is second on the list of most rushing yards among active players behind only Steven Jackson.

One thing about the Broncos is that they always seem to start slow and then pull away. Against the 49ers, they need to have a really good first half.

